com.datastax.oss.dsbulk.workflow.api

Interface WorkflowProvider

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CountWorkflowProvider, LoadWorkflowProvider, UnloadWorkflowProvider

    public interface WorkflowProvider
    A provider for Workflows. Providers are automatically discovered with the Service Loader API by the runner, see dsbulk-runner module.
